snippet.title: Wayfinder 1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
A Co-Op ARPG where you directly shape and customize the endless adventures you go on with friends, because Wayfinders are stronger together!

Wayfinder leaves Early Access, and with it hours of content. 

8 Unique Wayfinders to play as
20 Unique locations to explore and hunt foes
150 Weapons and their skins to collect
400 armor pieces to find and modify
300+ housing items to make Evenor your home

and so much more!

Wayfinder is a Co-Op APRG out now on Steam and PlayStation 5!
playwayfinder.com

http://twitch.tv/playwayfinder
